title: Garmin MapSource Tunisia v11 by 4x4travel.org
description:
Tunisia V11 (Topo and Auto) with simple auto-routing and topo lines!
MapSource version

Map Date: 15.08.2008
Manufacturer's homepage: <a href="
http://gps.4x4travel.org/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://gps.4x4travel.org/</a>

This routable map with topo lines contains all mountain- and sahara dirt
roads, most of the important roads (but not all, help with your
tracks!), many Pois like Campings, Fuel Stations, Hotels, rom. Ruins,
Nationalparks, Ksars, wells and other sight seeings!

The accuracy of this map is good because I use only GPS recorded tracks!
(I didn't vectorize in any way a raster map like other maps). The map is
very small with a lot of informations and very fast in the GPS device.

The autorouting is very simple (not that good compared to prof. maps.)
But you can use it for calculating distances. Don't use it in the cities
or highway!

The map is Trackware! Send me your tracks, but only tracks and waypoints
which are not already on the map.

Tracks: only from dirt roads and paved roads (not off road tracks). Good
quality (i.e. at least every 50 m a point).

Waypoints: Cities, Villages, Hotels, Restaurants, Fuel stops, Car
Services, wells (Sahara), nice picnic places, sight seeings, etc. etc.
All waypoints which are useful for the Tunisia traveller.

PS: If you have Tunisia  > V10 the existings installations will be overwritten!


This map is not locked.
It is free, updates can be also freely downloaded from the address above!
